testcase.title: verify response tags in getBiomarkerRecords response

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "query = cancer and queryLanguage = ssql and hits = 20" as parameter to "getBiomarkerUseResults" operation
I get a response with "20" integer values in tag "hits"
I get a response with "0" integer values in tag "offset"

testcase.title: verify response tags in getBiomarkerRecords response

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "query = Cancer OR NOT cancer and queryLanguage = ssql and hits = 20" as parameter to "getBiomarkerUseResults" operation
I get a response with "20" integer values in tag "hits"
I get a response with "0" integer values in tag "offset"
